reviewText: Still  my  favorite  ;  I  loved  the  comedy.  I  wish  people  would  get  past  problems they have  about stereotypes  etc.

This is the second purchase of the Amos & Andy Show I've ordered from you and enjoyed them.  The first one was the boxed set.  Watched the show as a kid and it was fun watching it again as an adult.  Thank you for your prompt service and quality of products.
